.TH CPPTEST 1 "February 2026" "3.0" "CppTest Manual"
.SH NAME
cpptest \- Advanced competitive programming testing utility
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cpptest
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fIFILE\fR] [\fIDIRECTORY\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Automated testing tool for C++. Supports test generation, stress testing, isolation, custom checkers, clang-tidy, and multiple compilers.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-S ", " \-\-stress
\fBStress Mode.\fR Requires \fIfast.cpp\fR and \fIgen.cpp\fR. Runs an infinite loop comparing the output of your solution against the brute-force solution on generated tests.
.TP
.BR \-G ", " \-\-no-gen-config
Ignore \fItests.cfg\fR file and use default generator settings (100 tests, args: -100 100).
.TP
.BR \-i ", " \-\-in-place
Run tests directly in the source directory.
.TP
.BR \-F ", " \-\-fix
\fBAuto-Fix Mode.\fR Automatically applies style fixes to the source code.
.TP
.BR \-R ", " \-\-no-comments
\fBRemove Comments.\fR Tests a temporary version of the code stripped of all comments.
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-fast
Skip static analysis (clang-tidy/format).
.TP
.BR \-K ", " \-\-force-checker
Force usage of \fIcheck.cpp\fR.
.TP
.BR \-k ", " \-\-force-diff
Force usage of standard diff.
.TP
.BR \-u ", " \-\-update
Self-update from GitHub.
.SH GENERATORS
If \fIgen.cpp\fR is present, it is used to generate \fI.in\fR files.
Configuration file \fItests.cfg\fR format: "Count Args" (e.g., "10 1 100").
Default: 100 tests with args "-100 100".
